        {
            "title": "雪佛龍、埃克森美孚盤前重挫;Levi Strauss飆升",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/F0m9iXdDFzAbivPD6Udegg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPED9Q177_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 美國股指期貨週三大幅上漲,此前美國總統唐納德·特朗普表示已與伊朗達成臨時停火協議,市場對中東戰爭結束的希望日益增強。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">與此同時,在特朗普表示美國已將原定對伊朗的打擊行動推遲兩週以促成長期停火後,油價暴跌超過13%。油價下跌有助於緩解市場對能源引發通脹飆升的擔憂,重新引發市場對聯準會今年稍後可能再次降息的押注。美國政府債券收益率下跌,緩解了股市面臨的部分下行壓力。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">截至美國東部時間05:55(北京時間17:55),標普500指數期貨上漲179點,漲幅2.7%。納斯達克100指數期貨上漲842點,漲幅3.5%,道瓊斯指數期貨飆升1,213點,漲幅2.6%。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-01e69de9-5061-3d27-8571-e9711d9f984a-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">以下是今日盤前美股主要個股動態:</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><ul class=\"mb-module-gap\"><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">能源股下跌,反映停火消息後油價的跌勢。雪佛龍(Chevron)、埃克森美孚(Exxon Mobil)、Venture Global、西方石油(Occidental Petroleum)和康菲石油(ConocoPhillips)均大幅下跌。</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">另一方面,航空股上漲,包括聯合航空(United Airlines)、達美航空(Delta Air Lines)、美國航空(American Airlines)和西南航空(Southwest Airlines)。</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">金價上漲也支撐礦業股。在衝突期間,由於市場押注利率將在更長時間內維持高位,金價一直受到壓制。紐蒙特黃金公司(Newmont Gold Corp.)、<span><span>巴里克黃金</span></span>(<span><span>Barrick Mining</span></span> Gold)和阿格尼科鷹礦(Agnico Eagle Mines)上漲。</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">金融股上漲,包括摩根大通(JPMorgan Chase)、高盛(Goldman Sachs)、美國銀行(Bank of America)和摩根士丹利(Morgan Stanley)。</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">CF Industries和Nutrien下跌,此前數週因伊朗戰爭導致化肥價格飆升而受到提振。</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美股七巨頭股票上漲——Meta Platforms、特斯拉(Tesla)、Alphabet、英偉達、亞馬遜(Amazon)、微軟(Microsoft)和蘋果(Apple)。</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">牛仔褲製造商Levi Strauss飆升,此前該公司上調了全年調整後每股收益和營收預測,第一季度財報表現也優於預期。</p></li></ul><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%9B%AA%E4%BD%9B%E9%BE%8D-%E5%9F%83%E5%85%8B%E6%A3%AE%E7%BE%8E%E5%AD%9A%E7%9B%A4%E5%89%8D%E9%87%8D%E6%8C%AB-levi-strauss%E9%A3%86%E5%8D%87-120637639.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-08 20:33:53",
