            "title": "〈智慧顯示展〉創為精密結盟友來新能源布局鈣鈦礦應用 鎖定三大AIoT領域",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"214\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/AF.bHAnoNHUuA1kRy6DsiQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTcwNTtoPTM5Nw--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/cnyes_hk_559/f53d23a1d0a0e2960c4c1fe0e47d8103\" width=\"380\"/></div></figure></div>",
